org.osmdroid.samplefragments.milstd2525

Class Plotter

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • org.osmdroid.samplefragments.BaseSampleFragment
        • org.osmdroid.samplefragments.data.SampleGridlines
          • org.osmdroid.samplefragments.milstd2525.Plotter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ListPicker.Callback

    public class Plotter
extends SampleGridlines
implements ListPicker.Callback
    A sample that provides two ways to plot single point MIL-STD 2525 icons
    • Via direct user input, enter the symbol code, then the icon is plotted at screen center
    • Via searchable picker, icons can then be plotted via long press
    TODO
    • More support for modifiers and attributes
    • Multipoint symbols
    created on 12/22/2017.
